[Multi-functional Shelves] This bookshelf is not only a simple storage shelf, but also a great display shelf. You can use it to showcase your dolls, models, antiques, potted plants, wines, and more in any room of your home, such as the kitchen, living room, study room, bedroom, or office.

[Easy Setup] Instruction and tools included, each piece is labeled, just follow the diagram instructions to assemble it step by step, it is recommended that two people assemble it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 22, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars easy assembly, looks good, pretty sturdy
reviews.reviewText: This shelf unit was well packaged and arrived in good condition...and, remarkably, had every piece of hardware in the package (about 60 screws) and all pieces properly marked with stickers. The instruction manual is picture-based but is clear and easy to follow. The shelves are not real, solid wood, this is noted in the description, but they look very good. The metal frame elements have a brown finish that has a sort of orange finish under the brown, there are scratches and rubbed areas on the finish that shows the orange-ish color....is it supposed to look "distressed"?-- but it is not enough of an issue to return (see photos), I doubt that there would be any difference with a replacement. I may try to touch them up sometime with a brown marker but again, it is a minimal issue.Some important assembly tips:1. Look very carefully at the diagrams to match the assembly of the metal frame parts and be sure you have the shelves oriented properly (the back and sides of each shelf have the wood edge around them.). The diagrams are surprisingly accurate. The first metal frame parts to assemble have different screw holes on the front and back sides so be careful to assemble these components carefully...if they are not put together right and you have to go back, it is easy to do so BECAUSE YOU FOLLOWED THE MOST IMPORTANT INSTRUCTION, which is #2....2. Heed the instruction advice which is on every page of the manual: DO NOT tighten the screws, give them enough turns to be sure they won't fall out but do not tighten....there are too many parts with multiple screws and the square metal frame will need to flex somewhat during assembly to get everything together. Resist the temptation to tighten them until the end!3. A "manual" hex wrench is included, it works but it will take you forever if you use it. Use a manual ratcheting screwdriver or socket wrench that works with standard (it's either a 1/8 or 5/32") hex insert and you will save a ton of time and hand fatigue.4. Don't use a drill with a hex bit in it for the screws unless you use it at the end for final tightening. it will turn the screws too quickly and tighten them too much, which will keep the frame from being able to have the slight flex needed to get every screw properly threaded. Best to use the manual ratchet, not the electric drill.5. There are two included, small "straps" meant to attach the shelf to the wall using wall anchors (enclosed, but they are just plastic and I would not trust them to prevent a tip-over.) I chose not to anchor the unit, so I placed the heavy stuff on the bottom and used the floor levelers (included) to get the unit level (used a level on the shelves to get it as level as possible.). If you choose to anchor it to the wall, get a high quality pair of anchors or moly bolts.NOTE: This is an honest review and not a result of any incentive. I did receive a post card asking to earn a gift card but this review was written as soon as I assembled the unit but was not posted due to wanting to add the photos. A gift-card offer arrived before posting but did not change anything and I don't know if it is even legit. I do like this unit and was sure to point out the frame scratches and the sturdiness which earned a "4".

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Rolanstar Bookshelf: A Stylish and Functional Addition to Any Space!
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the Rolanstar 5-Tier Industrial Bookshelf, and I couldn't be happier with my choice. This 71.8''H large bookcase offers a perfect blend of style, functionality, and durability, making it an excellent addition to my home.The open-shelf design is both visually appealing and practical, providing easy access to my books and decorative items. The five spacious tiers offer ample storage space, allowing me to display a variety of items without feeling cluttered or disorganized.The industrial design of the Rolanstar Bookshelf adds a touch of sophistication and elegance to my living space. The combination of metal and wood materials creates a rustic yet modern aesthetic that complements various decor styles. It has become a striking focal point in my room, garnering compliments from guests.Assembly of the bookshelf was straightforward and hassle-free, thanks to the clear instructions and included hardware. The sturdy construction ensures that the bookcase remains stable and can support the weight of my books and other items without any issues.In conclusion, the Rolanstar 5-Tier Industrial Bookshelf has exceeded my expectations in terms of style, functionality, and durability. It has transformed my living space, providing an attractive and practical storage solution for my books and decorative items. If you're looking for a stylish and functional bookshelf, don't hesitate to give the Rolanstar Bookshelf a try – you won't be disappointed!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very Nice Shelf
reviews.reviewText: This is one of the best purchases I have made. The quality for the $$ is fantastic. Super easy instructions to put together. The overall look is amazing. Looks much more expensive than it was. Nice to find a shelving unit that is wide but not just steel.

Overall this wasn't difficult to assemble. Took just over an hour by myself.Make sure you have a drill for the screws or it will take much longer by hand with a screwdriver or the little Allen keys they provide.The bookshelf is well made. Little product stickers remove easily and it looks fantastic as a backdrop for my YouTube videos.Very satisfied.
lovely shelf, easy to assemble, very stable and excellent quality

reviews.reviewTitle: Perfect fit for what I needed!
reviews.reviewText: Very good quality, easy to assemble and looks super nice. Good value for money and makes my funko pops look great on it!

I was worried about some of the reviews having challenges with building this shelf, but luckily the unit I got was perfect. It was very easy to assemble and everything lined up without issue. This shelf feels very strong and sturdy, thoigh I highly recommend using the provided wall anchors as it's also very heavy.The reason I gave 4 instead of 5 is because of the stickers they use. There are several stickers on the unit such as the warning label, parts label and a large "this side up" label on each shelf. As other reviews mentioned, these labels are difficult to remove cleanly and require soaking in goo gone (or similar adhesive remover) to get them off.Minor inconvenience in the grand scheme. Overall very happy woth it.
